{"tid":2347042,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得連登個圖片模式唔太方便 ?","createTime":"2020-12-30T17:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T19:16:37.000Z","uid":366509,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"19c98b4fa0aac778f634123e67f234e21950e027","tid":2347042,"uid":366509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T17:06:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gist.github.com/py3thon/ff795b24613bc2010750872c0a61ca7b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgist.github.com%2Fpy3thon%2Fff795b24613bc2010750872c0a61ca7b&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=82605d69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gist.github.com/py3thon/ff795b24613bc2010750872c0a61ca7b</a><br />\n<br />\n安裝說明<br />\n1. 安裝 Tampermonkey<br />\n2. 撳上面條 link<br />\n3. 撳個 raw button<br />\n4. Tampermonkey 會彈出頁面<br />\n5. 撳個 安裝 button<br />\n<br />\n影片說明<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/gz710h\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fgz710h&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=1ada8f23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/gz710h</a><br />\n<br />\n使用說明<br />\n1. 只要見到呢版就會記底睇緊邊張圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kKgpG6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkKgpG6e.png&h=aa2cfa20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.之後去到圖片模式就會搵返個張圖附近個行<br />\n<br />\n原因<br />\n整嚟係想自己追多圖 post 時可以開圖片模式揀完圖睇埋留言<br />\n之後再開 圖片模式 會係上次睇到邊行<br />\n<br />\n附上圖 link<br />\n乃木坂46討論區#455：距離紅白仲有四日<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/rNzACKX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/rNzACKX</a><br />\n<br />\n缺憾<br />\n1. 呢個位左右撳轉上下張圖係唔識記底, 只係會記得撳開張圖嘅第一次<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kKgpG6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkKgpG6e.png&h=aa2cfa20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 撳 F12 可以見到係不斷監聽個網, 未知點先可以撳開張圖先監聽<br />\n<br />\n3. 一定未係最慳資源同最好嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n請求好心人幫我改良, 等我可以加快我追post 追圖 追留言嘅速度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81899b4f43e11836e29e5d6d9d134c1272c8976","tid":2347042,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T17:09:52.000Z","msg":"連登啲class name 唔係會不停咁轉既咩"},{"pid":"467b5067403a60543be83ab155cc362718f7d636","tid":2347042,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T17:11:41.000Z","msg":"點解唔用regex match url<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a584503ed7517dbc6378570799db0437be035b","tid":2347042,"uid":366509,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e81899b4f43e11836e29e5d6d9d134c1272c8976","tid":2347042,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T17:09:52.000Z","msg":"連登啲class name 唔係會不停咁轉既咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T17:13:20.000Z","msg":"唔知..."},{"pid":"2abdc3c7964e89cbef2e072f97fa03337d7c2227","tid":2347042,"uid":366509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"467b5067403a60543be83ab155cc362718f7d636","tid":2347042,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T17:11:41.000Z","msg":"點解唔用regex match url<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T17:14:58.000Z","msg":"regex 好似好難搞, 我依家係轉返同 thumbnail link 一樣算"},{"pid":"2ea758241b3fee193923e015da1bf34dcd593bef","tid":2347042,"uid":246823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T17:16:21.000Z","msg":"陣間幫你執執佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132fb38e4192ed59726c26f2f78d57aaea8c57d8","tid":2347042,"uid":366509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ea758241b3fee193923e015da1bf34dcd593bef","tid":2347042,"uid":246823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T17:16:21.000Z","msg":"陣間幫你執執佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T17:16:30.