dly-gallery%2Fblob%2Fmain%2Findex.js&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=e79c60e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/wood-factory-j/lihkg-user-friendly-gallery/blob/main/index.js</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"個 file 要係 .user.js 尾先可以 activate 到 tampermonkey.<br />\n<br />\n同埋係咪多左<br />\n圖片模式 highlight 張圖<br />\n&amp;<br />\n記錄每個 post 最後睇既圖去local storage <br />\n呢兩個功能?<br />\n<br />\n但係依家好似係 post 撳圖而唔係圖片模式撳圖會 save 唔到."},{"pid":"d5c8de31431f58072ca15cf538888e663f19c7ad","tid":2347042,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19c98b4fa0aac778f634123e67f234e21950e027","tid":2347042,"uid":366509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T17:06:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gist.github.com/py3thon/ff795b24613bc2010750872c0a61ca7b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgist.github.com%2Fpy3thon%2Fff795b24613bc2010750872c0a61ca7b&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=82605d69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gist.github.com/py3thon/ff795b24613bc2010750872c0a61ca7b</a><br />\n<br />\n安裝說明<br />\n1. 安裝 Tampermonkey<br />\n2. 撳上面條 link<br />\n3. 撳個 raw button<br />\n4. Tampermonkey 會彈出頁面<br />\n5. 撳個 安裝 button<br />\n<br />\n影片說明<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/gz710h\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fgz710h&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm8eYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=1ada8f23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/gz710h</a><br />\n<br />\n使用說明<br />\n1. 只要見到呢版就會記底睇緊邊張圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kKgpG6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkKgpG6e.png&h=aa2cfa20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.之後去到圖片模式就會搵返個張圖附近個行<br />\n<br />\n原因<br />\n整嚟係想自己追多圖 post 時可以開圖片模式揀完圖睇埋留言<br />\n之後再開 圖片模式 會係上次睇到邊行<br />\n<br />\n附上圖 link<br />\n乃木坂46討論區#455：距離紅白仲有四日<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/rNzACKX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/rNzACKX</a><br />\n<br />\n缺憾<br />\n1. 呢個位左右撳轉上下張圖係唔識記底, 只係會記得撳開張圖嘅第一次<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kKgpG6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkKgpG6e.png&h=aa2cfa20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 撳 F12 可以見到係不斷監聽個網, 未知點先可以撳開張圖先監聽<br />\n<br />\n3. 一定未係最慳資源同最好嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n請求好心人幫我改良, 等我可以加快我追post 追圖 追留言嘅速度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T14:40:59.000Z","msg":"1.應避開用隨機classname做. code一update就要跟住update<br />\n2.冇test過以下code<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">(f un ct io n  ()  {\n\n        v ar  i ma ge;\n\n        //  Ge t  t he at er  m od e  p ag e\n        c on st  t he at erPa ge  =  '._1AEEI1g oa gMu9r5fVYt-Y4';\n\n        //  Se le ct  t he  n od e  t ha t  w il l  b e  o bs er ve d  f or  m ut at io ns\n        c on st  t ar ge tNo de  =  d oc um en t.b od y;\n\n        //  Op ti on s  f or  t he  o bs er ve r  (w hi ch  m ut at io ns  t o  o bs er ve)\n        c on st  c on fi g  =  {  c hi ldLi st:  t ru e,  s ub tr ee:  t ru e  };\n\n        //  Ge t  p ho to  m od e  p ag e\n        c on st  p ho toMo dePa ge  =  '.qS4Io sr432bIbXc jt pG0p';\n\n\nc on st  p ho toMo deW='._2h xZqJYY6uRl iNkPo rCiY5[d at a-s rc*=&quot;://&quot;]';\nc on st  t he at erMo deW='._32NDPFy_2eAc nGr d40_6My&gt;a[h re f*=&quot;://&quot;]';\n        //==  Ge t  p ho to  m od e  i ma ge  a nd  s cr ol l  ==\n\n        //  Sc ro ll  p ho to  i nt o  v ie w  i n  p ho to  m od e\n\nc on st  f un c1=(e lm)=&gt;(e lm.g etAt tr ib ut e('d at a-s rc').i nc lu de s(i ma ge)?(e lm.s cr ol lIn toVi ew()||t ru e):f al se);\n        f un ct io n  p ho toMo de()  {\n                        v ar  t ag s  =  d oc um en t.q ue rySe le ct orAl l(p ho toMo deW);\nAr ra y.f ro m(t ag s).s om e(f un c1)||c on so le.l og('n o  i ma ge');\n\n        }\n\n        //==  Ge t  t he at er  m od e  i ma ge  ==\n\n        //  Ge t  i ma ge  l in k  f ro m 